CustomField.description: Unique identification number assigned to each LinkedIn™ company page. It cannot be changed and is used as an “address” for the company page. This ID is useful because it never changes, even if the vanity URL changes. PipeLaunch uses this ID to improve the matching algorithm.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Unique identification number assigned to each LinkedIn™ company page. Used to improve PipeLaunch matching algorithm. Example: www.linkedin.com/company/12345678
CustomField.label: LinkedIn™ Numerical Id
